            Update a movie.
            </summary>
            <remarks>
            Send the Movie data in HTTP Request's body as JSON.
            URI Id and Movie Id within JSON should match.
            </remarks>
            <param name="id">Movie Id</param>
            <param name="movie">Movie Data</param>
        </member>
